---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="404 | Nomi Journal" description="Requested page was not found.">
  <Header />

  <main class="main-shell">
    <section class="container-shell">
      <div class="grid min-h-[calc(100vh-240px)] content-center justify-items-center gap-3 text-center md:min-h-[calc(100vh-280px)] md:gap-4">
        <p class="text-[86px] font-bold leading-none tracking-[-0.05em] text-zinc-900 md:text-[164px]">404</p>
        <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.42] text-zinc-700 md:text-[22px]">요청하신 페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다.</p>

        <div class="flex w-full max-w-[420px] flex-col items-center gap-2 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center sm:gap-3">
          <a href="/" class="btn-pill-dark w-full sm:w-auto">메인으로</a>
          <a href="/posts" class="btn-pill-soft w-full sm:w-auto">글 목록</a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 md:text-base">또는 검색으로 원하는 글을 찾아보세요.</p>

        <section class="page-card mt-2 w-full max-w-[904px] p-3.5 text-left text-xs leading-[1.5] text-zinc-600 md:text-[13px]">
          <p>공통 상태: loading · empty · error · 404</p>
          <p>A11y: h1 1개, 키보드 포커스, 대비, 대체텍스트</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
